## Objectives
- Increase quality of recommendations
- Improve recommendation acceptance rate
- Drive application starts and submissions
- Provide explainable, transparent guidance
- Maintain student trust through ethical AI

## KPIs
- **recommendation_accept_rate**: % of shown recommendations that students accept/save
- **rec_to_application_start**: % of accepted recommendations that lead to application start
- **application_start_to_submit**: % of started applications that are submitted
- **student_satisfaction_score**: CSAT from post-interaction surveys

